{"tid":1472272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO 就算可以轉 BC 請附加條例，三代做過警狗不適用","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:12:52.000Z","uid":31320,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"00f2c55ed5cf796e268e099245abaeb0596ed765","tid":1472272,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"雖然冇乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c12a2ff5bd3bb507bc3a9bb18a092433800a55","tid":1472272,"uid":226569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00f2c55ed5cf796e268e099245abaeb0596ed765","tid":1472272,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"雖然冇乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:03:06.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ca455b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1 : 簽咗咁多聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> / 英國佬唔會幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /英國佬都唔想收咁多新移民喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Q2: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 （ ff住先）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ4: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ca455b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"da03057b6ca88a7de8d466a8a7202740f49f75b3","tid":1472272,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:14:21.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<