萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支持?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.增加香港有外國國籍啲人數, 提升外國政府啲話語權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.因中共反對, 所以我地更加要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.中共話香港人都是中國公民, 唔通你地想一世都係中國公民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ca455b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"4846ada8b47c3e6e50fb1ff154b18e4850cb3dc4","tid":1472272,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b440e2448e9abc776c08700b7554815e5f53654e","tid":1472272,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"求求00後都幫手簽, 對你地都有好處<br />\n<br />\n英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支持?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.增加香港有外國國籍啲人數, 提升外國政府啲話語權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 